title: Nebulous.Series3.[2008].BBC_Radio_comedy.ogg.radioCat
description:
PROFESSOR NEBULOUS

The year is 2099. Professor Nebulous returns with his team of inept eco-trouble shooters in the third series of this hilarious sci-fi sit com.

NEBULOUS 3 continues the adventures of K.E.N.T. - the Key Environmental Non-Judgemental Taskforce in their struggle against alien threat and eco-logical disaster.

Like some strange collision of Doctor Who, Quatermass and Hitch Hiker&#039;s Guide To The Galaxy, series two beams back in with more monsters, more mayhem and more bizarre and inventive plots.

Starring Mark Gatiss of the multi award winning League of Gentlemen as the brilliant but erratic Professor Nebulous, ably supported by the show&#039;s writer Graham Duff (Ideal) along side Rosie Caveliero (Spoons) and Paul Putner (Little Britain).

Originally broadcast BBC Radio 4
